episode_details.title: Special Episode: Revisiting The Implications of AI in 2025 - S01 Recap & Deep Dive

S02 E11 - Ashton Tuckerman - The art and science of marketing - how to reconcile the intangible human side of the job with to cold hard facts of the digital industry, and why it's important to be a part of the conversation
S02 E10 - Alex Boyd - LinkedIn, Services, Saas and the people who love them - a deep dive into business building, channel analysis and the psychological challenges we face in digital work
S02 E09 - Stu speaks to Amanda Behre about the mid-career challenges we face in marketing, her new business Dear Thrive, and how the last few years of turmoil are shaping us both at work and in life
